{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_11_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――セミファイナルの数日前",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……凄くいいわ、この衣装。正直、感動してる\n{user}さんも感想を聞かせてくれる？",
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7336956184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺も同じ感想です。……でも今は何より、この衣装が\nセミファイナルに間に合ったことに感動してます",
      "startTime": 18.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.648638773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、悪かったわよ……この衣装を間に合わせるために\n貴方が凄く頑張ってくれたことは知ってるわ",
      "startTime": 25.9479141871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1176645438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "貴方には、本当に感謝してる。私の無理を聞いてくれて\nそして、約束を守ってくれてありがとう",
      "startTime": 35.3812482833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.0145828883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私もちゃんと守ったわよ、約束。次はセミファイナル\n――相手は、TRINITYAiLEね",
      "startTime": 47.0145828883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。星見プロのアイドル同士の\nそして、二回目の対決……ですね",
      "startTime": 53.2000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.632042424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。今度は、私達LizNoirが勝つわ\nでも貴方は、どっちが勝っても複雑な気分よね",
      "startTime": 64.0249689419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.2035157681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで{user}さん、その……\n瑠依達、セミファイナルではどんな衣装を着るのかしら",
      "startTime": 72.1916356086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなことを聞くんですか？",
      "startTime": 77.2402729194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9162137827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "その、用意してもらって今更なんだけど……\n私達の新衣装、思っていた以上に出来が良かったから",
      "startTime": 84.0405475616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.3226990224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけ新しい衣装を着るのは、なんだか……\nフェアじゃないかも、って気がしてきたのよ",
      "startTime": 93.8072142283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9211794695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依達も新しい衣装を着てステージに立つのなら\n私も心置きなく戦える、と思って聞いてみたの",
      "startTime": 100.6072142283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "デビューした時の衣装を着るそうですよ\n今まで応援してくれたファンに応えるため、だそうです",
      "startTime": 108.3666679383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.7602045538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの……。確かに、コアなファンは喜ぶでしょうし\nここ一番でのチョイスとしては、悪くないわ。でも……",
      "startTime": 118.6442332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.4773705008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワが新衣装でセミファイナルに臨むことは\n瑠依達も知っていますし、こうも言ってました",
      "startTime": 126.1775965356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "「この衣装は、勝利のために選んだものです」\n「新しい衣装だから有利、だなんて思わないことです」",
      "startTime": 133.6781326831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.3900010271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ、言ってくれるじゃない\nおかげで吹っ切れたわ。ありがとう",
      "startTime": 143.239574178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "フェアかどうかを気にして、全力を出せなかったら\nそれこそ瑠依達に失礼よね。勝ちに行くわ。全力で",
      "startTime": 149.4062388102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.7295676393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……葵は戻って来ませんけど、本当に三人でこの衣装を\n着るんですか？　莉央さんは、それでいいんですか？",
      "startTime": 158.833334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4651207767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "いい訳ないでしょ。でももし私が「葵が戻るまで\n新しい衣装は着ない」なんて言ったら――",
      "startTime": 168.7280963897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "きっと葵は喜ばないわ\n「つまらないことにこだわるんだね」って言われそう",
      "startTime": 175.0614266712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.7078151545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ははっ、葵なら本当にそう言いそうですね",
      "startTime": 178.7078151545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "私が、勝つための努力を怠るような真似をしたら\n葵は喜ばない。私が葵の立場でも、そう考えるもの",
      "startTime": 188.6679578144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.6211254122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "それに、セミファイナルまでに葵が戻って来る可能性は\nゼロじゃないわ。……私、諦めが悪いの",
      "startTime": 198.2012911478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（……莉央さんがそう信じているなら、俺も信じよう）\n（葵の分の衣装も、念のため用意しておくか）",
      "startTime": 207.8666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――セミファイナル前夜",
      "startTime": 212.3496379538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 213.6229722663
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 213.6829590801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（ついに明日、か。リズノワとトリエルの二回目の戦い）\n（勝ち残れば、いつかぶつかることは分かっていたけど）",
      "startTime": 220.8333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（いざその時が来ると、複雑な気分だな……）\n（俺の立場上、どちらか一方に肩入れは出来ない）",
      "startTime": 229.8999992371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3858.9469277000035,
          "startTime": 233.7589461648
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 233.7589461648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　偶然ね。{user}さん\n仕事帰りかしら？　遅くまでお疲れ様",
      "startTime": 236.7223004023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 240.445114009
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
